<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.8">
<l>nātta ḻumpa nāṉmukaṉu mīcaṉu māymuṟaiyā</l>
<l>lētta vaṅkō rāḷariyā yiruntavam māṉatiṭam</l>
<l>kāytta vākai neṟṟolippak kallatar vēykkaḻaipōy</l>
<l>tēytta tīyāl viṇcivakkuñ ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the lord, who sat there as a man-lion as by turns</l>
<l>Four-faced [Brahmā] and Īśa praise [him] so that their tongues bruise,</l>
<l>Is Lion-Man Mountain where the sky reddens with fires</l>
<l>Where [withered] bamboo stalks move and scrape [each other]</l>
<l rend="indent">along rocky pathways as dry mimosa pods rattle.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
